Late Nite Chef Fight - Season 1, Episode 8




Snakebite & Red

Laila Ali and Vic "Vegas" Moea host a culinary battle between two of Vegas's most salty chefs. Featuring exotic stash meats, everyone's temperatures rise as no one wants to lose and be forced to cook the winner's meal. Spike Mendelsohn and Chris Oh judge three rounds.
